data.text: —review as per photos— grilled chicken ramen: the ramen was quite delicious but personally (and i guess only this time) the season of the soup maybe need a little more kicker on shoyu because it felt a little bit flavorless and i like the chicken even more if they made it more crispy (maybe crispy wasn’t the right word) on its skin  all of the sushi: the sushi was fine and very much enjoyed it  and because it’s someone’s lucky day a.k.a birthday they as well served a free birthday cake sushi
